Perfect combination of style and function

The matte black finish provides a clean silhouette while serving functional comfort in your home or office.

Automatically adjust speed base on temperature

Keep your Vornado performing for years to come by cleaning dust off the front grill, air inlets, and blade, with access provided by a removable grill.

Simple, convenient controls

Three speed settings conveniently located on the base of the unit allow you to dial in your comfort.

Circulate all the air in the room

A Vornado circulator uses special airflow called Vortex Action to circulate all the air in the room. The air flows fast, cool and constant to create a cooling experience unlike any other.
